  <li>Name the application ‚Äúoauth2tutorial‚Äù<br />
<img src="/~cs110x/static/img/lab5/image2.png" alt="image2" /></li>
  <li>Next we will set up the web hosting functionality in Parse.
    <ul>
      <li>Select <strong>Hosting</strong> from the left side navigation bar in oauth2tutorial App Settings<br />
<img src="/~cs110x/static/img/lab5/image3.png" alt="image3" /></li>
      <li>In the Web Hosting section select the text box and type a unique name for your site eg. ‚Äúmy-awesome-site‚Äù<br />
