<h2 id="section-5-next-you-will-need-to-download-and-install-parses-command-line-tool">Section 5: Next you will need to download and install Parses command line tool</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Parse offers a powerful command line tool that provides you the power to create and manage your database without the hassle of dealing with servers. This can be accomplished via there Cloud Code framework accessed via command line tools.</li>
  <li>Visit the below link for details on Cloud Code
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://parse.com/docs/cloud_code_guide">https://parse.com/docs/cloud_code_guide</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>To install command line tool on Mac/Linux type the following command
    <ul>
      <li>‚Äúcurl -s https://www.parse.com/downloads/cloud_code/installer.sh | sudo /bin/bash‚Äù<br />
<img src="/~cs110x/static/img/lab5/image7.png" alt="image7" /></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

