  </li>
  <li>Replace the Parse application id and javascript key in <strong>views/head.ejs</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>The Keys can be found on your Parse application page <strong>Settings=&gt;Keys</strong><br />
<img src="/~cs110x/static/img/lab5/image15.png" alt="image15" /><br />
<img src="/~cs110x/static/img/lab5/image16.png" alt="image16" /></li>
      <li>Remove the public folder
        <ul>
