<h2 id="section-9-uses-for-oauth">Section 9: Uses for OAuth</h2>

<ul>
  <li>The functionality of OAuth can be extended to a multitude of different websites such as Facebook and Google +</li>
  <li>OAuth can be used on a variety of platforms such as android and IOS.</li>
  <li>Finally OAuth is independent of Parse and can just as easily but used with your own local databases as well.</li>
</ul>

